title: GET_DISPLAY_NAME_FROM_VEHICLE_MODEL
content:
0xB215AAC32D25D0190xEC86DF39// GetDisplayNameFromVehicleModel
char* GET_DISPLAY_NAME_FROM_VEHICLE_MODEL(Hash modelHash);Parameters:modelHash: A vehicle model to check.Returns: The display name for the vehicle, or 'CARNOTFOUND' if invalid.Returns the display name/text label (gameName in vehicles.meta) for the specified vehicle model.
